This new-gen anime depicts shorter form of most popular sport Football(Soccer) in the world. This is a 5-a-side game where positions are ala,fixo,pivo,golerio etc. 
A guy named Haru yamato joins Koyo Academy High school's Futsal team led by Japan U18 team member Toi Tsukioka. Haru admires Tsukioka's former U18 teammate Tennoji 
desires to become like him. The story revolves around Haru and Sakaki, another first year at Koyo.
